- - pōca-k-kai
- n. prob. மோசம்+. (J.)
- 1. Deceptiveness of appearance;
- போலித்தோற்றம்.
- 2. Superficiality of character;  plausibility;
- மேற்பூச்சு.
- 3. Counterfeit;  sham;  pretence or cover to save credit or hide poverty;
- மாயம்.

